attributes.action: Creating Essex forest national park joining up with woodland in suffolk
attributes.additional_details:
The aim of this petition is to get the Government to agree onget  Essex  forest national park created in Essex planted  to join up with areas of woodland on the Suffolk board around hatfield forest and bishops Stortford  and st albans whicb could be created for rewilding species like

Red squirrel
European beaver
European lynx
European Bison
European moose
European Stork
European wild cat
Euroepan red deer
European wolverine
